#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rastermiscellaneous.rst:2
msgid "Raster miscellaneous"
msgstr "Rastro įvairūs"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rastermiscellaneous.rst:14
msgid "Build overviews (pyramids)"
msgstr "Kurti apžvalgas (piramides)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rastermiscellaneous.rst:15
msgid ""
"To speed up rendering time of raster layers overviews (pyramids) can be "
"created. Overviews are lower resolution copies of the data which QGIS uses "
"depending of the level of zoom."
msgstr ""
"Norint pagreitinti braižymą, galima sukurti rastro sluoksnių apžvalgas "
"(piramides). Apžvalgos yra žemesnės rezoliucijos duomenų kopijos, kurias "
"QGIS naudoja priklausomai nuo mastelio."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rastermiscellaneous.rst:19
msgid ""
"This algorithm is derived from the `GDAL addo utility "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/gdaladdo.html>`_."
msgstr ""
"Šis algoritmas kilęs iš `GDAL addo įrankio "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/gdaladdo.html>`_."

